<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN Gothic?? ?Century FONT-FAMILY: 10pt; **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE:><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed </FONT>– This is almost just like being evaluated however these items the development team is totally undecided if they want to implement or how to do so.&nbsp; The Community Team plans to give updates on these types of items every 2 weeks, even if it’s just a “no change since the last update”<o<img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0>></o<img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-tongue.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0>></SPAN></P>
